{"tid":534284,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"突如其來的惡耗！《龍珠超》動畫慘遭腰斬即將播映完畢","createTime":"2018-01-19T15:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T05:36:05.000Z","uid":64694,"like":9,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d9786db78e261a7c330af7d1ca2320b81bd5eac8","tid":534284,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"正當大家繼續熱烈討論着《龍珠超》裏力之大會的劇情時，今天對各位龍珠迷來說卻是一個惡耗的到來。根據日本報道及《龍珠超》官方證實，《龍珠超》動畫將於 4 月暫停播放，即是現時《宇宙生存篇》將會是動畫的終章，第 131 回是最後的一回。而 4 月同樣時間將會播放《鬼太郎》動畫。消息傳出去《龍珠超》的作畫師亦同時表示第 126 回原來是他最後一次的負責。對於這突如其來的消息，各位龍珠迷相信也一時不能接受得到，而那邊廂鳥山明已着手構想第 20 部《龍珠》劇場版電影，並將於今年 12 月公映，那麼各位在《龍珠超》播映完畢後稍作休息，再期待劇場版電影的來臨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/1/dragon-ball-super-ending-anime-details?amp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2018%2F1%2Fdragon-ball-super-ending-anime-details%3Famp%3D1&d=bGv%2FDjm0j4UK7CCbfR7dsAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c1f9962b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2018/1/dragon-ball-super-ending-anime-details?amp=1</a><br />\n<br />\n作畫畫成咁，依家先斬咪算俾面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，之後拍劇場版電影算啦，你拍電影我實會入戲院睇，起碼d畫唔會崩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/234319_889f169f0758ddb7d2376dafd9306cf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F234319_889f169f0758ddb7d2376dafd9306cf8.jpg&h=1e3168e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/234324_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F234324_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=40a743c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2c7ecdfca26e70484a9e85d466252f71bf9b602","tid":534284,"uid":60050,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T15:54:51.000Z","msg